{"problem_id": 12159, "annotation": "xiaokaizhang_2023-03-06", "source": "GeoQA-length-12563", "problem_level": 1, "problem_text_cn": "如图，在△ABC中，∠ACB＝90°，AB＝2，延长BC到点D，使BD＝3CD，若E是AC的中点，则DE的长为（）", "problem_text_en": "", "problem_img": "12159.png", "construction_cdl": ["Polygon()", "Collinear()", "Cocircular()"], "text_cdl": [], "image_cdl": [], "goal_cdl": "", "problem_answer": "", "theorem_seqs": [], "raw_choices": ["1.5", "√{2}", "1.5", "1"], "raw_answer": "【解析】∵∠ACB＝90°，∴∠ECD＝90°，∴E是AC的中点，∴AC＝2CE．∵BD＝3CD，∴BC＝2CD，∴\\frac{AC}{CE}=\\frac{BC}{CD}=2，∴△ABC∽△EDC，∴DE=0.5×AB=1．故选：D．", "raw_label": 4, "raw_formal_point": ["相似三角形的判定与性质"], "raw_comment": "本题主要考查相似三角形的判定与性质，解答的关键是熟记相似三角形的判定定理：两边对应成比例且其夹角相等的的两个三角形相似．"}